items.name: 2023H1
items.description:
Applicator's 2023 the first half (H1) seminar

Date: from 2023-6-4, to 2023-9-4 
Purpose: promoting and sharing basic knowledges

Opening words
This is the first seminar since the establishment of the society
Thank you for participating
Seminars were held to share and develop each other's knowledge
Seminars on sympathetic topics are held in public

Through consultation with undergraduate researchers, seminars on AI technology will be held across the board
● Machine Learning
● Computer Vision
● Reinforcement Learning

In addition, the seminar will be held with topics related to basic programming and contents that will help the project progress

Thank you for your interest
from, 2023H1 seminar leader devhoodit


Applicator, Society in Seoul National University of Science and Technology, Dept. of Applied Artifical Intelligence
